## Additional Terms

### Ethical Use Clause

This software is designed to assist with job applications, not to automate them
completely or to spam recruiters. Users of this software agree to:

1. Review all AI-generated content before use
2. Manually submit all job applications
3. Respect each company's application policies
4. Not use the software to bypass security measures (CAPTCHA, etc.)
5. Not use the software for mass unsolicited outreach
6. Comply with all applicable laws and regulations

The authors and contributors of this software disclaim all responsibility for
misuse of this tool. Users are solely responsible for how they use this software
and must ensure their use complies with applicable laws and ethical standards.
